 loop: [
  "? reread the repeated HTML families before declaring any attribute redundant",
  "< normalize the static landmark skeleton first so runtime behavior sits on honest HTML",
  "$ let the runtime infer repeated bookkeeping instead of copying it page by page",
  "^ keep the semantic vocabulary meaningful by preserving the attributes that actually drive behavior",
  "% prefer one canonical region contract over parallel HTML, CSS, and JS guesses",
 ]
